Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: Aliens on the Oregon Trail Edition with Beer City Bruiser!! 

It has been a week of unusual Alien theories, A.I. dying, and ghosts being accepted as normal in the world of the paranormal and Tim and Bruiser have hitched the wagons and got the families ready and also prepared news stories for you!

This week,  Evidently, As Canada says it is going to share it's UFO info with the US, Experts are suggesting that alien civilizations keep collapsing before they can reach Earth ! A new study suggests that paranormal experiences are the norm, not the exception, The world's first cyborg has died, and a Japanese company is making custom coffins for vampire fans!
